RESOLVED, the Board of Visitors approves the proposed memorial to Frederic
                       W. Scott, to be located on McCormick Road adjacent to the first year
                   dormitories, and thanks Frederic W. Scott, Jr., for his generosity;

RESOLVED, that the Board of Visitors of the University of Virginia approves the
                   replacement of gift funding with University debt in the Rouss Hall Renovation
                   and Expansion Project;

list.item:
1. The University reasonably expects to reimburse
                       expenditures from the issuance of tax-exempt debt to be issued by the
                       University incurred for the project;

